data.description: Welcome to 21535 Whittington Street, a house that could be your perfect new home. This spacious property offers a multitude of features and upgrades that are sure to impress. Situated on a big lot, this house provides ample space and privacy. The fenced-in backyard is ideal for children or pets to play freely, giving you peace of mind. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by solid oak doors that exude elegance and quality craftsmanship. The interior boasts beautiful oak engineered hardwood floors that add warmth and sophistication to every room. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with stunning granite countertops that make meal preparation a breeze. The updated vanities in the bathrooms provide a modern touch, while the new oak trim throughout the house adds a touch of luxury. Not only is this home aesthetically pleasing, but it also offers practical features. The new insulated garage door ensures optimum temperature control for you. Enjoy natural light and privacy with the faux wood blinds on the kitchen, bedrooms, and bathroom windows. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms, this property offers plenty of space for your family or guests. Conveniently located in a desirable neighborhood, this property is in proximity to schools, shopping centers, and parks. Commuting is a breeze with easy access to major highways. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a home that combines style, functionality, and convenience. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and see for yourself why 21535 Whittington Street should be your next address.
